                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Careful</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, red (vivid red and strong red)</seg>
                        Scribe: Gabra ʾAmlāk. Gabra ʾAmlāk
                        is mentioned as the scribe in a supplication on <locus target="#36rb">36rb</locus> and in the concluding supplication on <locus target="#80va">80va-</locus>vb.<date>20th century (?)</date>
                        <list type="abbreviations">
                           <item>Throughout Text I-4</item>
                           <item>ለዓ፡ ዓ፡ አ፡ for ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡</item>
                           <item>ለዓ፡ ዓለ፡ አ፡ for ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡</item>
                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; name of the scribe; names of the
                           donors (in a secondary hand); groups of lines in the incipit page of
                           Texts I-1; incipit of sections and subsections; elements of the
                           punctuation signs and of the text dividers; elements of Ethiopic
                           numerals.</seg>
                     </handNote>
